  <refentry xml:id="function.atan" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
   <refnamediv>
    <refname>atan</refname>
    <refpurpose>反正切</refpurpose>
   </refnamediv>
 <refsect1 role="description">
  &reftitle.description;
   <methodsynopsis>
    <type>float</type><methodname>atan</methodname>
    <methodparam><type>float</type><parameter>arg</parameter></methodparam>
   </methodsynopsis>
    <para>
     返回 <parameter>arg</parameter> 的反正切值，单位是弧度。<function>atan</function> 是
     <function>tan</function> 的反函数，它的意思是在
     <function>atan</function> 范围里的每个值都是
     <literal>a==tan(atan(a))</literal>。
    </para>
   </refsect1>
   <refsect1 role="parameters">
  &reftitle.parameters;
  <para>
   <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
     <term><parameter>arg</parameter></term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       要处理的参数
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
  </para>
 </refsect1>
 <refsect1 role="returnvalues">
  &reftitle.returnvalues;
  <para>
   <parameter>arg</parameter> 的反正切弧度。
  </para>
 </refsect1>
 <refsect1 role="seealso">
  &reftitle.seealso;
  <para>
   <simplelist>
    <member><function>tan</function></member>
    <member><function>atanh</function></member>
    <member><function>asin</function></member>
    <member><function>acos</function></member>
   </simplelist>
  </para>
 </refsect1>
  </refentry>

